" scroll the viewport faster
nnoremap <C-e> 5<C-e>
nnoremap <C-y> 5<C-y>

" window movement
nnoremap <C-H> <C-W>h
nnoremap <C-J> <C-W>j
nnoremap <C-K> <C-W>k
nnoremap <C-L> <C-W>l

" quick quoting
nnoremap <Leader>q" ciw""<Esc>P
nnoremap <Leader>q' ciw''<Esc>P
nnoremap <Leader>q( ciw()<Esc>P
nnoremap <Leader>q) ciw()<Esc>P
